<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10200011>
    dc:description "FIGURES 48–52. Harpactea bilgenur sp. nov. 48. Bulb (left), prolateral view 49–50. Ditto, retrolateral view 51–52. SEM photos of the bulb, nearly retrolateral view. Arrows in figures 50 and 52 point to the chitinized dentition at the tip of the conductor. Abbrevation: C, conductor; E, embolus; T, tegulum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10200011/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10200013>
    dc:description "FIGURES 53–54. Harpactea bilgenur sp. nov. 53–54. Vulva, dorsal view. Abbrevations: AA, anterior margin of the anterior arch; AC, anterior arc; E, embolus; PD, posterior diverticulum; RS, roundishstructure; S, spermatheca; SK, spermathecal keel; T, tegulum; TB, transversal bar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10200013/files/figure.png" ;
